Text:
Thanks for this Tymex. Never heard these groups before. This group remind me of a more-melodic version of Einsturzende Neubaten, very intense and original sounds.

I love those drums of Ausgang as well, there is a whole series of punk groups which have that tribal thing going on. Most of them have been influenced my Killing Joke I believe. 

I'll keep these seeding when your connection goes down. Cheers.
